General.Name: Future First Technologies Limited
General.Description: Future First Technologies Ltd engages in building of digital platforms in Australia. The company offers Asset Vision platform, a cloud-based digital platform, provides a real-time view of how assets are being inspected, maintained, and managed, as well as picture of compliance and contractual obligations; and FARMBUY, a real estate portal for searching rural properties. The company was formerly known as PS&C Limited and changed its name to Future First Technologies Ltd in October 2020. Future First Technologies Ltd was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
